Usage:
'dm <password>

The command allows a player character to become a dungeon master. The server must be configured to allow the player to become a dungeon master or else the message "Sorry Pal, I don't think so." is displayed.

Upon success, the server responds:
The Dungeon Master has arrived!
Ok, you are the Dungeon Master!

All players in the game see a "The Dungeon Master has arrived!" message.

See also: [help]nodm[/help]
See also: [help]dmhide[/help]
See also: [help]dm_commands[/help]
